Additionally, the paper uses network science to analyze swarm-based systems, which falls under the category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses the flexibility and scalability of swarm-based systems, which are related to the field of artificial intelligence, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another possible category.
